noteOff() - Method in class com.craigl.softsynth.EnvelopeGenerator
A noteOff event completes the envelope generation process and returns
the EnvelopeGenerator to the idle state awaiting the next noteOn event.
noteOn() - Method in class com.craigl.softsynth.EnvelopeGenerator
This method is called to initiate the envelope generation process.
The state machine transitions through the attack, decay and sustain
states then awaits the noteOff event.
